Analytics

Our AB testing & analytics engine has been built from the ground-up for e-commerce brands. We run true split tests that can be precisely targeted. We collect the data that matters for your business, help you understand the confidence in the outcomes, and share all the data for deep analysis.

Discover Analytics

No Guesswork

True split tests mean that you are getting apples-to-apples data. Our statistical significance engine gives you confidence in results.

Measure Revenue & Profitability

Track results to the individual order - allowing you to measure how tests impact conversion, revenue, and profitability.

Results at a Glance

Intuitive dashboards make it easy to understand how groups are performing. Roll out “winners” straight from the dashboard

Full Transparency

Easily export raw data to dig into detail. Integrate with Google Analytics to get a full picture of your data
